Dialogue: 1,0:00:46.93,0:00:49.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,孩子们好  现在播出的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.93,0:00:49.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, kids, it's time for
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.47,0:00:53.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝如你所愿精品特辑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.47,0:00:53.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob's "You Wish" Spectacular Special
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:53.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345.969,305.478)}如你所愿
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.63,0:00:54.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.63,0:00:54.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurray
Dialogue: 1,0:00:54.70,0:00:57.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在有请如你所愿的主持人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:57.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now the host of "You Wish"
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.84,0:01:01.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他有着比基德船长更蓬松的灯笼裤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.84,0:01:01.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's got puffier pantaloons than Captain Kidd
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.15,0:01:04.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有着比黑胡子更卷的胡须
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:04.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and fuzzier facial hair than Blackbeard
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.26,0:01:06.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就是全美最爱的海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:06.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's America's favorite pirate
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.08,0:01:09.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恩斯诺的派斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:09.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patchy of Encino
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.36,0:01:21.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好  粉丝同伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.36,0:01:21.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, fellow fanatics
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.98,0:01:23.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到我家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:23.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to me quarters
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.33,0:01:25.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不你们来厨房吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.33,0:01:25.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come on back to the galley
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.02,0:01:27.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今天在给你们整点消遣的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:27.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm cooking up a real treat for you today
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.37,0:01:30.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打进来投出票时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:30.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's calling-in vote time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.68,0:01:32.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们今天来选择我们动画片的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.68,0:01:32.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You get to choose how our cartoon ends today
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.95,0:01:33.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以用电话来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.95,0:01:33.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,via the phone
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.74,0:01:35.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者用互联网来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:35.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or the Internet
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.74,0:01:37.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要你们有这么个技术条件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:37.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you're technologically inclined
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.11,0:01:41.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在这部动画片跟大多动画片不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.11,0:01:41.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, this cartoon is different from most cartoons
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.38,0:01:41.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不一样在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.38,0:01:41.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in that
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.98,0:01:42.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么个不一样法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.98,0:01:42.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In what way?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.45,0:01:46.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这不就是我的没意思小跟班
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:46.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't my less-than-amusing sidekick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.25,0:01:47.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鹦鹉波蒂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:47.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty the parrot
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.56,0:01:49.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂  跟观众们打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.56,0:01:49.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty, say hello to the nice people
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.65,0:01:50.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.65,0:01:50.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.30,0:01:51.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是被强行关押在这的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.30,0:01:51.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm being held here against my will
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.95,0:01:52.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:52.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.86,0:01:56.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:01:56.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty, come back
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.23,0:01:57.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.23,0:01:57.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.80,0:01:59.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:01:59.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.30,0:02:01.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:01.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where'd you go?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.43,0:02:02.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.43,0:02:02.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.57,0:02:04.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在里面吗  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.57,0:02:04.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You in there, buddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.44,0:02:06.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.44,0:02:06.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.94,0:02:07.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.94,0:02:07.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.41,0:02:14.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放我出去  你个坏鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.41,0:02:14.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get me out of here, you scurvy bird
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.99,0:02:31.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚刚说到哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.99,0:02:31.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, what was I saying?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.73,0:02:33.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这部动画片不像是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:33.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, this cartoon ain't like
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.99,0:02:36.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们看的那种旱鸭子版动画片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.99,0:02:36.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,most of your "landlubbing" cartoons
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.87,0:02:38.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这部动画片不止有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:38.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This cartoon has not one
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.62,0:02:39.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也不止有两个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:39.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not two
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.39,0:02:41.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而是三个不同的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.39,0:02:41.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but three different endings
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.14,0:02:43.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我让你们拨打
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:43.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, when I tell you to call
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.10,0:02:46.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,425,,屏幕下方滚动的电话号码
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:44.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,401,,the number that's scrolling down there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.61,0:02:46.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,401,,at the bottom of the screen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:57.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(362.014,351.722)}不好意思  原版电话号码\N去戴维琼斯柜子里安度晚年了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.83,0:02:47.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,425,,现在还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:47.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,401,,No, not now
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.32,0:02:50.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,425,,让你们打了才能打
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.32,0:02:50.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,401,,Don't call till I tell you to
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.03,0:02:52.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,425,,播动画片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:52.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,401,,Roll the cartoon
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.51,0:02:55.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,425,,记得要在最后投票  因为
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:55.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,401,,Now, remember, to vote at the end because
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.52,0:02:59.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非得不让我好过是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:02:59.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna make this easy, are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.03,0:03:00.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安静
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:00.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quiet
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.55,0:03:03.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快停下  晩点再响起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:03.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Avast there, belay that ringing
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.17,0:03:03.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别响了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:03.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.90,0:03:05.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要让我疯掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.90,0:03:05.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's driving me mad
