Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.22,0:03:30.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海草哥麦片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:30.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kelpo
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,内含八个奖品之一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"With one of eight essential prizes inside"
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.44,0:03:46.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是见鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.44,0:03:46.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy Shrimp
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.37,0:03:48.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:48.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.11,0:03:50.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上天从我麦片盒里生小孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:50.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The sky had a baby from my cereal box
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.99,0:03:53.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:53.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.85,0:03:55.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上天生小孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:55.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The sky had a baby
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.33,0:03:58.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个不是小孩  是大锚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:58.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not a baby, that's a giant anchor
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.11,0:03:59.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:03:59.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, go away
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.04,0:04:00.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.04,0:04:00.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.02,0:04:01.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上天生小孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:01.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The sky had a baby
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.86,0:04:02.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:02.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.69,0:04:04.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说该给人家起什么名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:04.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think we should name it?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.09,0:04:05.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:05.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.60,0:04:07.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不你们两个去爬锚绳去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:07.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you two go climb its anchor rope?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.99,0:04:10.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它一定会通往很远的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:10.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it goes somewhere far away
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.23,0:04:14.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看你们干的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:14.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now look what you've done
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.80,0:04:16.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是我们干的  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:16.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We didn't do it, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.08,0:04:17.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可清白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:17.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our hands are clean
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.70,0:04:19.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,清白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:19.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clean
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.67,0:04:22.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我倒要刨根问底查个明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:22.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going to get to the bottom of this thing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.32,0:04:23.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是问顶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:23.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that be the top?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.05,0:04:28.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:28.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squid, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.15,0:04:28.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:28.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.58,0:04:32.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,33,,几英寸后
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.12,0:04:35.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:35.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ship
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.15,0:04:39.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你到底要胡思乱想多久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:37.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, how long are you going to stay
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:39.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in your little fantasy world?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.42,0:04:40.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:40.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, look
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.19,0:04:42.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的有大船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:42.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a giant ship
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.23,0:04:43.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了  我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:43.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great, let's go
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.71,0:04:47.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于能给这乱扔大锚的来一点教训了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.71,0:04:46.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I can finally give this anchor-dropper
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:47.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a piece of my mind
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.47,0:04:48.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉不太好  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:48.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.97,0:04:52.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那艘船周围有可怕的绿光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:52.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That ship has a spooky green glow around it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.44,0:04:53.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能就是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:53.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's probably because
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.67,0:04:55.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船主实在是游手好闲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:55.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,its good-for-nothing owner is too lazy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.64,0:04:59.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,懒得打扫  锚也不好好放
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:59.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to clean or drop his anchors in the right place
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.84,0:05:01.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:01.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squid, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.38,0:05:06.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁是这木头箱子的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:06.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, who owns this crate?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:07.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(323.907,281.467)}主人
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.29,0:05:09.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:09.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on out
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.05,0:05:11.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要投诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:11.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to file a complaint
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.83,0:05:18.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这地方是不是感觉很熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:18.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doesn't this place seem familiar?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.20,0:05:18.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:18.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.93,0:05:19.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.93,0:05:19.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.46,0:05:20.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:20.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:21.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\pos(488.368,404.191)}响 铃
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.10,0:05:21.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉就是有那么点印象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:21.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it just kind of ring a bell?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.06,0:05:26.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道谁是这船的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:26.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know who owns this boat
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.20,0:05:27.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是想不起名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:27.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just can't place the name
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.14,0:05:30.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(434.216,219.216)}飞天魔鬼所有
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.81,0:05:35.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错了  名字不叫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:35.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, it's not
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.72,0:05:42.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是飞天魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:42.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am the Flying Dutchman
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.42,0:05:44.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:44.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.39,0:05:47.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  这船是红男爵的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:47.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This ship belongs to the Red Baron
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.63,0:05:52.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁胆敢在飞天魔鬼的地盘打扰人家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:52.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who be disturbing the Flying Dutchman in his own lair?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.23,0:05:53.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.23,0:05:53.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lt's Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.15,0:05:54.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他要投诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:54.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He wants to complain to you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.73,0:05:56.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我我我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:56.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I-I-I
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.30,0:05:57.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可可可没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:05:57.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I-I-I don't
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.72,0:06:02.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你骂人家船脏人懒又是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:05:59.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, what about all that stuff about him
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:02.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,having a dirty ship and being lazy and all?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.38,0:06:04.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可没说过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:04.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I-I never said that
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.94,0:06:06.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,侮辱一个人的船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:06.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Insulting a man's ship
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.99,0:06:09.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比侮辱一个人的妈更严重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:09.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,be worse than insulting his mother
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.85,0:06:10.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错了  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.85,0:06:10.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.74,0:06:12.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚骂的是他妈脏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:12.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it was his mother you said was dirty
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.52,0:06:13.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是船脏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:13.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not his ship
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.16,0:06:18.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一个是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:18.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're next
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.76,0:06:24.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是差一点就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:24.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was a close one
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.90,0:06:27.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:27.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome back
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.03,0:06:31.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是差一点点就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:31.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was a closer one
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.44,0:06:33.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:33.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome back
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.57,0:06:38.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们两个怎么每次捣乱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.57,0:06:38.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How come when they act up
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.04,0:06:39.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都要欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:39.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all they get is the welcome wagon?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.96,0:06:41.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要我说  早就
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:41.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you ask me, it's
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.85,0:06:46.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你们要不要再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:46.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So are you going to try that again?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.65,0:06:47.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:47.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Probably
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.65,0:06:51.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:51.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about now?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.46,0:06:53.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  他们不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.46,0:06:53.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, they're not
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.26,0:06:58.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.26,0:06:58.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now listen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:06:59.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(533.494,299.253)}鬼矩手册
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.70,0:07:04.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无论是谁登上了飞天魔鬼的船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:04.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Whosoever sets foot on the Flying Dutchman's ship
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.16,0:07:06.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管是不是不请自来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.16,0:07:06.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"uninvited or otherwise
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.65,0:07:10.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都要成为他的鬼水手  一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:10.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"shall become members of his ghostly crew forever
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.04,0:07:12.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.04,0:07:12.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.31,0:07:12.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永远
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:12.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ever"
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.31,0:07:15.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会领名片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:15.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will we be getting business cards?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.68,0:07:16.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别吵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:16.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Silence
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.28,0:07:18.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们现在是我的鬼水手了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:18.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're part of my crew now
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.82,0:07:22.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的工作就是四处航行吓唬别人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.82,0:07:22.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and our job is to sail around and frighten people
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.19,0:07:24.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会很累人  麻木人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:24.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lt'll be grueling, mind-numbing
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.56,0:07:25.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还反反复复的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:25.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and repetitive
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.22,0:07:26.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差不多就像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:26.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just like
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.56,0:07:29.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,白天的电视节目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:29.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,daytime television
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.69,0:07:31.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在你给我听好  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:31.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, you listen here, mister
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.96,0:07:33.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要是真觉得我会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:33.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you think I'm going to
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.20,0:07:36.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这垃圾堆里待个五分钟以上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:36.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,spend more than five minutes on this dumpster
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.06,0:07:37.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就想多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:37.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then you're crazy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.54,0:07:39.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒是看看这地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:39.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, look at this place
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.54,0:07:41.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:41.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's disgusting
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.71,0:07:42.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁教你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:42.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whoever told you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.81,0:07:45.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要把油灯放硬木板边上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:44.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that hanging oil lamps
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:45.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,next to hardwood paneling was a good idea
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.81,0:07:47.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.81,0:07:47.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.41,0:07:48.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要给我看东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:48.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I suppose you're going to show me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.21,0:07:49.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是好好看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:49.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, that's very nice
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.15,0:07:51.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这什么玩意  魔术表演吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:51.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is this, some kind of magic act?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.99,0:08:07.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁还要进去飞天绝望里玩一玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:07.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would anyone else like to enter the Fly of Despair?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.30,0:08:08.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:08.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.24,0:08:10.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们明白自己地位了  飞天魔鬼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:10.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we know our place now, Mr. Dutchman
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.09,0:08:11.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会照你说的做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:11.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll do anything you say
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.90,0:08:14.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么你们俩新来的可以  擦甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:14.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then for starters, you can swab the deck
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.67,0:08:16.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.67,0:08:16.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.56,0:08:19.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,活生生的鬼拖把
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:19.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a real, live ghost mop
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.53,0:08:21.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有这顶帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:21.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I got this hat
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.09,0:08:21.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:21.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.01,0:08:24.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们今晚要去裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:24.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're heading down to Bikini Bottom tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.52,0:08:26.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来闹个鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:26.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for a little haunting spree
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.45,0:08:30.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我要这艘船的外观非常吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:30.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I want this ship to look good and scary
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.39,0:08:33.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说你要船的外观非常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:33.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean you want it to look good
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.73,0:08:34.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.73,0:08:34.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and scary
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.97,0:08:36.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们也许可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:36.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I think we could probably
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.03,0:08:37.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:37.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.10,0:08:39.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,人家说的是要外观特别好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:39.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think he means he wants it to look so good
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.90,0:08:41.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好到可怕的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:41.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that it's scary
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.53,0:08:43.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者可能是让船的外观很吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:43.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or maybe that by looking so scary
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.87,0:08:45.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就可以忽略掉船很难看了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:45.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you forget that it doesn't look good
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.50,0:08:47.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:47.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't get it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.57,0:08:48.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:48.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, it's easy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.31,0:08:48.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,意思就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.31,0:08:48.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It simply means
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.94,0:08:50.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别管什么意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:50.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never mind what it means
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.79,0:08:52.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,样子吓人就行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:52.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just want it to look scary
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.92,0:08:53.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:53.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.91,0:08:54.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是那种
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:54.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.71,0:08:58.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天花板发霉  水池里有虫爬的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:58.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,mold growing on the ceilings, bugs in the sink
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.12,0:09:00.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你不要船好看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:09:00.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, you don't want it to look good?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.42,0:09:01.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点干
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.42,0:09:01.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get moving
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.72,0:09:02.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水手的命儿真是妙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:02.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A sailor's life is a wonderful life
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.92,0:09:04.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,命儿实在妙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:04.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A wonderful life for sure
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.03,0:09:09.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚夜色真美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:09.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a night be this
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.89,0:09:11.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水手们  跟我嚎叫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:11.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Crew, howl with me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.80,0:09:15.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让七大洋颤栗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:15.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so that we might set the seven seas ablaze with fear
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.83,0:09:44.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:44.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That'll do
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.83,0:09:46.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  方家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:46.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, square one
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.51,0:09:48.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然粉家伙在负责航行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.51,0:09:48.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Since pink one's working the navigation
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.75,0:09:51.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就让你来找我们第一个受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:51.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's up to you to find our first victim
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.24,0:09:56.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给  用这把望远镜找
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:56.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, use this spyglass
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.34,0:09:59.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:09:59.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, hurry up
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.07,0:10:00.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时间不等人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:00.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're burning moonlight
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.95,0:10:03.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看能找到谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:03.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see who we can find
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.25,0:10:08.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船长  那边那位可以吓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:08.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Captain, there's a guy we can scare
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.52,0:10:15.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有四块饼干  吃掉了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:15.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I had four biscuits, and I ate one
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只有三块了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then I only had three
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.36,0:10:22.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看到有小孩子夜不归宿让我开心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:22.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It does me heart good to see children out after dark
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.57,0:10:25.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,粉家伙  给我们带到石头后边去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.57,0:10:25.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pink one, take us behind those rocks
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.71,0:10:27.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到石头后边去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:27.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Moving behind the rocks
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.71,0:10:31.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:31.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep going
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.69,0:10:34.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:34.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're good, you're good
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.71,0:10:35.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:35.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.75,0:10:36.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:36.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,stop
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.18,0:10:37.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  船长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:37.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Cap'n
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.98,0:10:39.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会把划痕弄干净的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.98,0:10:39.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll buff out those scratches
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.25,0:10:42.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  那个别管了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.25,0:10:42.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, never mind it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.83,0:10:45.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给暗号你们就跳出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:45.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just jump out when I give the signal
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.96,0:10:53.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:53.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Prepare to be burdened
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.06,0:10:57.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我的鬼海盗们留下挥之不去的阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:57.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with the haunting memory of my ghostly ghost pirates
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.14,0:11:01.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,暗号就那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:01.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Was that the signal?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.14,0:11:03.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:03.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, sorry, sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.52,0:11:04.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:04.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just do it again
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.84,0:11:10.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我的鬼海盗们留下挥之不去的阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:10.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With the haunting memory of my ghostly ghost pirates
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.19,0:11:22.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:22.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How does he do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.60,0:11:27.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回船上去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:27.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back on the ship
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.00,0:11:32.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这还是个谜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:32.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's still a mystery
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.97,0:11:35.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那些人真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:35.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those guys are dorks
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.52,0:11:37.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  不过是我的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:37.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, but they're my dorks
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.64,0:11:40.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:40.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're good, you're good
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.09,0:11:53.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.09,0:11:53.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're good, you're good
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.19,0:11:54.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:54.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're good
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.93,0:12:05.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:05.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're good, you're good
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.79,0:12:25.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得飞天魔鬼干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:25.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why do you think the Dutchman
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.98,0:12:27.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫我们在卧铺里等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:27.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,asked us to wait in our bunk room?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.69,0:12:29.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能是他要给我们奖励
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:29.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's going to give us a reward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.74,0:12:31.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比如说电影票吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:31.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like movie passes?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.01,0:12:32.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者是超大咖啡杯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.01,0:12:32.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or an oversized coffee mug
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.53,0:12:38.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,经过考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:38.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.44,0:12:39.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:39.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop bouncing
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.04,0:12:45.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你们一辈子当我船员好像行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:45.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This whole "crew for eternity" thing isn't working out
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.73,0:12:48.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,与其说是你们的问题  不如说是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:48.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not really you, so much as it is me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.58,0:12:49.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要放了我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:49.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're setting us free?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.98,0:12:52.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实吧  我要吃掉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:52.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, actually, I'm just going to eat you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晩餐见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you at dinner
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.09,0:12:57.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:57.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.96,0:12:59.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:12:59.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.92,0:13:00.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:00.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.41,0:13:00.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.41,0:13:00.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.49,0:13:03.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:03.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's leave
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.06,0:13:04.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是门锁上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.06,0:13:04.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But the door is locked
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.50,0:13:06.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,唯一的出路是穿过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:06.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the only way out is through the
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.00,0:13:08.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,香水商店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:08.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,perfume department
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.67,0:13:15.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这么干了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:15.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's do it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.37,0:13:44.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我讨厌从那走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.37,0:13:44.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I always hate going in there
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.07,0:13:45.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:45.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.91,0:13:47.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  你听
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:47.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, listen
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.27,0:13:48.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲爱的日记
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:48.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dear Diary
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.44,0:13:51.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟他们讲我明天要吃掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:51.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l've told them I'm going to eat them tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.40,0:13:52.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做了那种棕酱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:52.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l made up some of that brown sauce
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.98,0:13:55.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先前我表哥临时给我看过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:55.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my cousin showed me just for the occasion
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.98,0:13:58.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又找着我的饭点袜了  可真是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:58.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing I found my dining sock again
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.42,0:14:02.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还记得我上次丢了饭点袜不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:02.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember the last time I lost me dining sock?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.93,0:14:04.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当时我一整个星期都吃不下饭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.93,0:14:04.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I couldn't eat for a whole week
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.16,0:14:08.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊  有时我在想要是碰巧出了事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:08.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir, sometimes I wonder how I survive
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.23,0:14:10.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还怎么好好过日子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:10.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If anything should ever happen
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把我袜子还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me back my sock
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.37,0:14:18.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都清楚我没袜子吃不下饭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:18.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows I can't eat without it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.51,0:14:19.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不给
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:19.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.40,0:14:21.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:21.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, then
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.71,0:14:27.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.71,0:14:27.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give it to me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.41,0:14:27.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不给
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:27.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.06,0:14:28.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:28.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.51,0:14:30.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你会把弹性拉没的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:30.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're stretching out the elastic
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.23,0:14:32.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像陷入僵局了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.23,0:14:32.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It would seem we have reached an impasse
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.15,0:14:34.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,粉家伙说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.15,0:14:34.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pink one is right
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.82,0:14:35.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你们说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:35.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell you what
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.02,0:14:39.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们把袜子还我  我就给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:39.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you give me back the sock and I'll give you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.59,0:14:41.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.59,0:14:41.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,three wishes
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.13,0:14:42.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要五个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:42.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make it five
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.83,0:14:43.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.83,0:14:43.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Four
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.76,0:14:44.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:44.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.86,0:14:46.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要就拉倒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:46.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it or leave it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.00,0:14:48.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:48.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.90,0:14:49.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:49.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,three
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.87,0:14:51.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们有三个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.87,0:14:51.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You get three wishes
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.50,0:14:54.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有三个愿望  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:54.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three wishes, Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.06,0:14:55.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:55.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wishes?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.94,0:14:58.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真希望能早点知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:14:58.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish we had known that earlier
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.14,0:15:02.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  你们就剩下两个愿望了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.14,0:15:02.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, you got two wishes left
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.45,0:15:05.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啦  还有两个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:05.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we still have two more
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.13,0:15:07.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好激动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:07.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How exciting
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.54,0:15:09.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真希望章鱼哥能来亲眼目睹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:09.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish Squidward were here to see this
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.79,0:15:18.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴一切都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:18.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, I'm glad all that's over
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.90,0:15:22.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:22.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you're back
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.63,0:15:23.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你猜怎么着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:23.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess what
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.69,0:15:25.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞天魔鬼给了我们三个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:25.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Dutchman gave us three wishes
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.56,0:15:26.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星用了第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.56,0:15:26.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick used the first one
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.64,0:15:27.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:27.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I guess I
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.54,0:15:29.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用掉了第二个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.54,0:15:29.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just used the second one
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.57,0:15:32.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么最后一个是你们欠我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:32.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, then the last one you owe me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.04,0:15:34.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为你们又把我拖下水了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:34.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because you got me back into this mess
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.08,0:15:35.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢着  愿望应该是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.08,0:15:35.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, I think it belongs to me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.32,0:15:43.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都够了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.32,0:15:43.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's enough
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.16,0:15:47.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用我的神秘超凡力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:47.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Using my mystic otherworldly powers
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.53,0:15:50.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,由我来决定最后一个愿望归谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:50.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I shall decide who gets the last wish
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.36,0:15:54.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咿呢咪呢唛呢哞  抓住水手脚趾头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:54.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eenie-meenie-minie-mo, catch a sailor by the toe
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.20,0:15:55.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果大叫放他走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:55.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If he hollers, let him go
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.27,0:15:57.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我妈教导我要挑最好的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.27,0:15:57.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My mother told me to pick the very best one and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.34,0:15:59.30,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(359.006,362.394)}投票
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.87,0:16:01.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全体成员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:16:01.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All hands
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:00.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(359.006,362.394)}投票
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.22,0:16:02.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,投票时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:02.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to vote
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:02.81,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(359.006,362.394)}投票
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.39,0:16:03.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在来投票
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:03.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's voting time
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:04.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(359.006,362.394)}投票
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.24,0:16:07.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  动画片先播到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.24,0:16:07.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's our cartoon so far
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.36,0:16:09.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在让你们来决定结局
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:09.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now it's time for you to decide how it ends
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.88,0:16:12.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后一个愿望会花落谁家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:12.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who will get their last wish
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.00,0:16:14.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会是轻狂的章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:14.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will it be sassy Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.12,0:16:15.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是肥肥的派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:15.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Portly Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.30,0:16:17.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是好家伙海绵宝宝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:17.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or good old SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.22,0:16:20.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我忠心的船员正热切等候你们的来电
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:20.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My trusty crew is eagerly awaiting your call
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:32.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(362.014,351.722)}不好意思  原版电话号码\N去戴维琼斯柜子里安度晚年了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.21,0:16:26.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,425,,快把沙发上的锚拉起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:26.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,401,,So hoist your anchor off that couch
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.50,0:16:27.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,425,,速速开始投票
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:27.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,401,,and make with the votin'
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.74,0:16:29.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,425,,现在正是大好时机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:29.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,401,,This is your big chance
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.35,0:16:33.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,425,,广告过后马上揭晓胜利者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:33.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,401,,We'll be right back to announce the winner
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.74,0:16:36.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,孩子们好  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:36.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, children, I'm back
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.72,0:16:39.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望你们大家都把票投出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:39.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope all you boys and girls got your votes in
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.24,0:16:42.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为你们现在必须走甲板落海身亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:42.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because it's time for you to walk the plank
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.28,0:16:44.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,33,,请稍候
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.02,0:16:47.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:47.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, kids
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.11,0:16:48.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:48.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What I meant to say was
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.61,0:16:50.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在要来公布胜利者了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:50.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's time to announce the winner
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.09,0:16:55.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过首先  来看看落选的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:53.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But first, let's take a look
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:55.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,at the endings you didn't choose
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.52,0:16:58.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根据我们的高科计数器上写的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:58.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,According to our high-tech counterology
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.22,0:17:01.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,落选的有  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:17:01.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you didn't choose Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.13,0:17:05.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是先来看看要是派大星中选
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:05.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But let's see what Patrick would have wished for
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.59,0:17:06.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会许什么愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:06.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you'd picked him
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.97,0:17:10.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  播录像带
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.97,0:17:10.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, roll the tape
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.61,0:17:11.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,播录像带
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:11.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Roll the tape
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.14,0:17:14.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,播录像带
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:14.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,roll the tape
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.15,0:17:15.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,播录
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:15.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,roll
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.68,0:17:16.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:16.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, God
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.15,0:17:19.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我妈教导我要挑最好的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:19.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My mother told me to pick the very best one and
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.38,0:17:20.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:20.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.12,0:17:20.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:20.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.65,0:17:21.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:21.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.19,0:17:22.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,选到你了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:22.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's you, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.43,0:17:23.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:23.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make your wish
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.36,0:17:25.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  派大星听着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:25.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, Patrick, listen
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.95,0:17:27.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不太想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.95,0:17:27.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I do not particularly feel like
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.79,0:17:30.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一辈子都困在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:30.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,being trapped here for all eternity
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.07,0:17:33.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一辈子是一段非常长的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:33.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eternity is a very long time
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.43,0:17:34.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:34.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.63,0:17:36.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  一定要使劲想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:36.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you've got to think harder
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.80,0:17:38.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加倍努力使出吃奶的劲想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:38.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than you've ever thought before
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.10,0:17:41.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样没用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:41.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not gonna do it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.61,0:17:42.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再使劲想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.61,0:17:42.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think harder
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.71,0:17:44.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:44.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.82,0:17:45.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  快想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.82,0:17:45.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, think, think
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.54,0:17:47.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,使劲去想  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:47.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put on your thinking cap, come on
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.37,0:17:48.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  你也能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:48.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you can do it, too
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.68,0:17:49.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:49.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,come on, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.65,0:17:56.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我许好愿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:56.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.12,0:17:58.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的愿望实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:58.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your wish is granted
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.83,0:18:02.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:02.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.06,0:18:03.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要点口香糖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:03.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Want some gum?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.43,0:18:06.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你许愿要口香糖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:06.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You wished for gum?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.96,0:18:09.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是非得一辈子待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:09.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if we're gonna be here forever
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.81,0:18:12.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒不如让口气清新清新一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:12.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we might as well have fresh breath
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.37,0:18:18.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托  飞天魔鬼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:18.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Mr. Dutchman
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.43,0:18:19.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放我们出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:19.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let us out
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.63,0:18:20.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别这么坏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:20.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be so mean
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.41,0:18:23.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有薄荷味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:23.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Minty
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.40,0:18:24.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托放我们出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:24.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on let us out
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.58,0:18:29.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那派大星可让我震惊到假腿都在震了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:27.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That Patrick shivers me timbers
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:29.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,right down to my peg leg
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.06,0:18:35.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不选那个结局还挺对的  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:35.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were right not to pick that one, kids
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.18,0:18:37.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,简直就是胡扯  废话一通
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.18,0:18:37.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seemed like a lot of nonsense to me, malarkey
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.93,0:18:40.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  来看看另一个落选者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.93,0:18:40.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, let's take a look at the other loser
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.34,0:18:47.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来章鱼哥也落选了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.34,0:18:47.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It appears you didn't vote for Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.94,0:18:48.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没怪你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:48.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l don't blame you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.84,0:18:49.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也不会投他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:49.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have either
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.94,0:18:53.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但还是先来看看如果飞天魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:51.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But let's see what would have happened
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:53.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if the old Dutchman's
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.14,0:18:56.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点到了章鱼哥会怎么样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.14,0:18:56.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,meenie-minie-mo finger landed on Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.15,0:18:57.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:57.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.65,0:18:58.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:18:58.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.18,0:18:58.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:18:58.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.85,0:19:00.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你有愿望了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:00.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you get a wish
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.94,0:19:02.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,超棒的大愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.94,0:19:02.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A great big wish
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.59,0:19:05.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  知道我要许什么愿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.59,0:19:05.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right, and you know what I wish?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.56,0:19:06.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:06.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.40,0:19:08.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我希望我从前一生都没
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:08.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish that I had never met
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.66,0:19:12.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,见过你们两个呆头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:12.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you two barnacleheads before in my entire life
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如你所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Show me it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.83,0:19:16.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  貌似我们以前没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.83,0:19:16.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, there, I don't believe we've met
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.36,0:19:17.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我叫海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:17.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My name is SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.60,0:19:19.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我同伴派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:19.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and this is my associate Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.40,0:19:20.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:20.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.10,0:19:22.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是我的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.10,0:19:22.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.21,0:19:24.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  既然你们互相介绍完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.21,0:19:24.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, now that introductions are out of the way
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.90,0:19:26.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么就开饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.90,0:19:26.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's time for dinner
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.01,0:19:28.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚说你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.01,0:19:28.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what did you say your name was?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.62,0:19:29.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:29.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l'm Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.86,0:19:30.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:30.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm your neighbor
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.32,0:19:33.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴认识你  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:33.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.72,0:19:35.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看我们会有好多时间互相熟悉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.72,0:19:34.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll have plenty of time to get
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:35.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to get to know each other, I guess
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.99,0:19:41.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在就是万众期待的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:41.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now, the moment you've all been waiting for
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.22,0:19:44.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好把牛奶从鼻子里喷出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:44.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, get ready to blow milk out your nose
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.01,0:19:46.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为现在要公布胜利者了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:46.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'cause it's time to announce the winner
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.66,0:19:48.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,信封拿来  波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:48.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The envelope, please, Potty
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.71,0:19:50.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  我的乖鸟助理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:50.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, my fine-feathered assistant
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.37,0:19:52.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真想不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:52.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, what do you know?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.69,0:19:54.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胜利者是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:54.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The winner is
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.11,0:19:55.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:55.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:57.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(414.16,348.165)}胜利者
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.14,0:20:00.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂  闻到什么了没
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.14,0:20:00.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Potty, you smell something?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.88,0:20:03.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂  你脑袋装了引信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:03.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty, that fuse in your head
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.03,0:20:05.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都说过不耍特技了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:05.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you, we're not doing that stunt
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.65,0:20:07.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没收到备忘录
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:07.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't get the memo
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.29,0:20:13.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在是万众强推的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:13.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now the most requested ending
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.53,0:20:15.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:15.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.69,0:20:17.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:17.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.26,0:20:17.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.26,0:20:17.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.83,0:20:18.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.83,0:20:18.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.56,0:20:20.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在快想  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.56,0:20:20.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, think, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.43,0:20:22.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们就要被吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:22.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're about to get eaten
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.00,0:20:23.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以许什么愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.00,0:20:23.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What can you wish for
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.57,0:20:25.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以让我们不被吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:25.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to make it so we don't get eaten?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.14,0:20:28.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:28.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.52,0:20:30.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都想明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:30.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got it all figured out
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.08,0:20:31.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他不会吃掉我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:31.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He won't be able to eat us
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.87,0:20:35.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我希望飞天魔鬼是吃素的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:35.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because I wish that the Dutchman was a vegetarian
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.04,0:20:42.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:42.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.62,0:20:44.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.62,0:20:44.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're home
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.26,0:20:45.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:45.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did it, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.89,0:20:47.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:47.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're safe
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.16,0:20:49.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我们为什么变水果了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:49.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But why have we been turned into fruits?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.00,0:20:53.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也许了个愿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:53.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get a wish, too
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.63,0:20:56.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水果可以预防坏血病
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:56.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And fruit prevents scurvy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.67,0:21:02.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:02.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back here with that
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.42,0:21:03.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要逮着你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:03.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.35,0:21:16.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:16.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.32,0:21:20.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:20.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that, kids
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.72,0:21:22.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是派斯忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:22.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lt's just that old Patchy can't help
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.79,0:21:25.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,节目最后哽咽到说不出话来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.79,0:21:25.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but get all choked up at the end of a show
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.00,0:21:28.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过好消息就是  从现在起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:28.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But the good news is, from now on
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.32,0:21:30.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们像通常那样看旱鸭子版的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:30.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when you watch this cartoon "landlubbing" style
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.73,0:21:32.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这部动画片的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:32.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like you usually do
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.06,0:21:34.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就会有你们选到的结局了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:34.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it'd have the ending you picked
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.02,0:21:38.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在你们就是成功的正式动画策划了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:35.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, now you're an official
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.87,0:21:38.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,big-time cartoon decision-maker
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.25,0:21:44.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可别冲昏头了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.25,0:21:44.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just don't let it go to your head
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.09,0:21:46.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  波蒂来跟大家说晩安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.09,0:21:46.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yup, say good night to the folks, Potty
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.52,0:21:48.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.52,0:21:48.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.55,0:21:51.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.55,0:21:51.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I quit
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.99,0:21:55.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,节目就到这了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.99,0:21:55.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's it, folks
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.45,0:21:59.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得马上去办员工管理工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.45,0:21:56.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right now I've got a little
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.73,0:21:59.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,employee management to take care of
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.07,0:22:00.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.07,0:22:00.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Potty?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.66,0:22:02.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,波蒂  快进你的好笼子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.66,0:22:02.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potty, get in your nice cage
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.43,0:22:03.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.43,0:22:03.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think so
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.13,0:22:04.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,于是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:04.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And so
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.77,0:22:09.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝如你所愿精品特辑到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.77,0:22:09.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we conclude SpongeBob's "You Wish" Spectacular Special
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.27,0:22:12.34,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360.008,250.341)}感谢投票
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.21,0:22:10.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢投票
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.21,0:22:10.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for voting
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.57,0:22:11.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.57,0:22:11.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
